Role:
1. Development team: Give them ideas and tips
2. Customer: Talk to customers
3. Support team: Reduce load in support team. Give playbook to support team
to better quip them for solving problem.
4. Data science team: Get ideas from them using data.
5. PM vs PO: PM gives ideas. PO implements using tickets.
6. Design team: Better customer journey.
7. Sales team: Better customer journey and amplify product market fit.
8. Finance team: Cash view vs actural view. When we get paid and for what we get paid. When do we render that service.
